statisticslevel -- Control output level

Not intended for general use.
"statistics 0" (quiet mode -- useful for speed chess)
suppresses "W.command", "targ", and "hashes" output on SYSPRINT.
"statistics 1" is the default level of output.
"statistics 2" prints a line of statistics after each iteration
"statistics 3" prints summary statistics on SYSLIST.
"statistics 4" also prints individual iteration statistics.
